<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brilliant-adj">brilliant <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'brɪljənt/    美 /'brɪljənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>光辉灿烂的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>in the <strong>brilliant sunshine</strong> 
在明媚的阳光下</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>卓越的；杰出的；才华横溢的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a brilliant scientist / musician 
杰出的科学家/才华横溢的音乐家</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>brilliant idea</strong> / thought / design 
绝妙的主意／想法／设计</p></div>

<h4 id="3-bre">3.★ <strong>极好的 (BrE)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That’s quite brilliant! How did you do that, may I ask? 
太棒了！请问你是怎么做到的？</p><footer>人教⑧ – 4</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>brilliantly /'brɪliəntli/ adv   </p></div>